<body>

<main class="home-body">
    <div class="logo"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmks1qdth/image/upload/v1532826615/arm.png" height="400px"
            width="600px"></div>
    <div class="home-nav">
        <div class="home-blog">
            <a href="/blog">
                <h1>K.O.'s Tech Corner</h1>
                <h3>Begeinner Friendly Web Development and Computer Programming How-To's, Motivation, and Opinions.</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="home-tuts">
            <a href="/tutorials">
                <h1>Tutorials and Other Resources</h1>
                <h3>Some of the best computer programming and web development tutorials and courses I have found online
                    or in bookstores. Updated regularly.</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="home-news">
            <a href="/technews"><h1>Web Development and Computer Programming News</h1>
            <h3>A constantly updating stream of Web Development and Computer Programming news from some of the best sources online.</h3>
        </a>
        </div>
        <div class="home-tools">
            <a href="/tools">
                <h1>Useful Tools</h1>
                <h3>A regularly updated list of the best tools that I have found for computer programming and web
                    development.</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="home-grind">
            <a href="/grind">
                <h1>My Daily Grind</h1>
                <h3>Have a look at my Journey to Becoming a Web Developer, also quite a bit of me venting about one
                    thing or another. Updated daily with all of my progress.</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="home-contact">
            <a href="/contact-me">
                <h1>Contact Me</h1>
                <h3>Offer me work, ask me questions, criticize me, praise me. It's a Contact Page! You know what to do
                    with it!</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="home-about">
            <a href="/about">
                <h1>About Me</h1>
                <h3>Gather a little insight about the man that is Kenneth Olsen, learn what makes him tick, learn what
                    he like and dislikes, and above all else learn About Him.</h3>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="first-place">
        <h1>Winner of "The Best Web Developer Ever Award"</h1>
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmks1qdth/image/upload/v1535156659/bg1stplace.png" alt="Image of a blue, first place, ribbon">
        <h3>As voted by Nancy Olsen, My Mom</h3>
    </div>
    <h2 class="testimonials">Here are some testimonials from those who have seen my work.</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="dad-quote">
            <h3> Gary Olsen (Dad)</h3>
            <p><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i><i>It's about time he got out of my basement and is trying to find a
                    real job. HEY!! STOP EATING MY SALAMI AND CHEESE!!!</i><i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i></p>
        </div>
        <div class="mom-quote">
            <h3>Nancy Olsen (Mom)</h3>
            <p><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i><i>Oh. My BooBoo is just amazing at everything. Of course he won the
                    Best Web Developer Ever Award! I couldn't think of a better or more deserving web developer I have
                    ever met that would deserve it more.</i><i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i></p>
        </div>
        <div class="girlfriend-quote">
            <h3>Crystal Waucaush (Girlfriend)</h3>
            <p><i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i><i>Yeah. He's great at computer development.. <span>Me: Its Web
                        Development babe..</span> I mean Web Development.. Ok. I said it, can we go now?</i><i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="real-quotes">That's right!! Those are real quotes, from real people!!!</p>

